  "title": "Sales Executive (Machinery) - West - WCDT",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Supervised and followed up on enquiries, quotations, and related documentation with internal teams, contractors, and customers.</li>\n  <li>Ensured timely quotation submission and proper documentation handling before delivery arrangements.</li>\n  <li>Coordinated with customers and internal departments to resolve quotation and delivery-related issues.</li>\n  <li>Led assistants in gathering information and communicating delivery schedule changes or updates.</li>\n  <li>Checked and verified that equipment deliveries were completed accurately; gathered customer feedback for service improvement.</li>\n  <li>Investigated and resolved customer complaints regarding transportation, documentation, and missing or lost items.</li>\n  <li>Reviewed supplier quotations and verified purchase orders and approvals before submission.</li>\n  <li>Handled incoming calls and directed them to the appropriate personnel for assistance</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>**5 days work week.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>**possess own vehicle</strong></p>\n<p><strong>**Car Allowance, Transport Allowance, Sales Commissions provided.</strong></p>\n<p><strong>**AWS &amp; Bonus provided</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd | 20C0270</p>\n<p>Tew Jie Wei | R22106822 <br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<br>\n</p>",
